---
description: One-call diagnostic for the latest slow request — bundles request + trace waterfall + logs + SQL + N+1 detection.
---
Run `gofasta debug last-slow-request --json`. The result includes
`request`, `trace`, `logs`, `sql`, and `n_plus_one`. Walk through
each section and propose a fix. Requires `gofasta dev` to be
running (devtools tag enabled).
